hopobject.body: I was made redundant two months ago orlistat prescription cost Now, moving to guidance. Since Q3, total revenues finished according to our expectations. We are maintaining the midpoint of full year 2013 guidance of $5.190 billion and narrowing the range to between $5.175 billion and $5.205 billion representing year-over-year growth of 12% to 13%. Excluding pivotal and divestitures, our total revenue growth for 2013 is expected to be between 16% and 17%. Given our strong license revenue performance in the third quarter, license revenue for the full year is now expected to be within the range of $2.255 billion and $2.275 billion representing 8% to 9% growth as reported and 10% to 11% excluding pivotal and divestitures. In both cases, this represents an increase in the midpoint of guidance by approximately one half of a percentage point.
